QuestData.Title: One Drakonid's Junk
QuestData.Description: <A glistening pocket watch lays amongst the many piles of junk. Maybe Gryrmpech will know what to do with it.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the pocket watch to Gryrmpech in the Gardens.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the pocket watch to Gryrmpech in the Gardens.
QuestData.RewardText: This was in the shed? It's not mine, but I think I remember who it belongs to.
